'''聯合國安理會2199號決議'''，是於2015年2月12日在[[聯合國安全理事會|聯合國安全理事會]]上一致贊成而通過的法案。此份法案由[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]起草，使得各國具有法源針對恐怖主義份子實施[[經濟制裁|經濟制裁]]<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.euronews.com/2015/02/12/un-security-council-votes-yes-to-cutting-off-isil-funding/| title =UN Security Council votes yes to cutting off ISIL funding| publisher =[[歐洲新聞台|歐洲新聞台]]| date =2015-02-12| accessdate =2015-02-28| archive-date =2015-02-15| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150215023804/http://www.euronews.com/2015/02/12/un-security-council-votes-yes-to-cutting-off-isil-funding| dead-url =no}}</ref>。其中法案強調「依照[[聯合國憲章|聯合國憲章]]和[[國際法|國際法]]下採取一切打擊行動...[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]對國際和平與安全所引發的威脅」<ref name="un">{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/press/en/2015/sc11775.doc.htm|title=Unanimously Adopting Resolution 2199 (2015), Security Council Condemns Trade with Al-Qaida Associated Groups, Threatens Further Targeted Sanctions|publisher=[[聯合國|聯合國]]|date=2015-02-12|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2015-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218021009/http://www.un.org/press/en/2015/sc11775.doc.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

